videos.headline: Snoop Conner plunges in for an Ole Miss TD
videos.description: Ole Miss scores the first touchdown of the game as Snoop Conner gets in from one yard out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Snoop Conner plunges in for an Ole Miss TD) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lideatrick Griffin makes sensational catch for Mississippi State
videos.description: Lideatrick "Tulu" Griffin gets up and makes a sensational catch for Mississippi State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lideatrick Griffin makes sensational catch for Mississippi State) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Matt Corral spins into the end zone for big-time Ole Miss TD
videos.description: Matt Corral calls his own number and breaks a tackle for the 4-yard touchdown to extend Ole Miss' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Matt Corral spins into the end zone for big-time Ole Miss TD) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jett Johnson's 48-yard INT sets up Mississippi State's TD
videos.description: Jett Johnson picks off Matt Corral to set up Jaden Walley's 11-yard touchdown for Mississippi State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jett Johnson's 48-yard INT sets up Mississippi State's TD) 2021/11/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lane Kiffin lets Mississippi State fans know it's over after Ealy's TD
videos.description: Jerrion Ealy weaves through the defense to find the end zone for the 15-yard Ole Miss touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss hoists Egg Bowl trophy high after downing Mississippi State
videos.description: Ole Miss proudly shows off the Egg Bowl trophy after defeating Mississippi State 31-21.
